des:
Squaw Valley Alpine Meadows is an internationally renowned mountain resort in North Lake Tahoe. This skill enables you to ask questions such as, "What lifts are open today?", "What trails are open?", "Did it snow yesterday?", is "Is lift Red Dog open?" and more. For more on the resort, please visit: https://squawalpine.com/
